statements: SELECT * FROM user_activity
SELECT user_id, action_type FROM user_activity WHERE action_type = 'login'
SELECT action_type, COUNT(*) FROM user_activity GROUP BY action_type
SELECT timestamp, tool_used FROM user_activity WHERE user_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000'
SELECT * FROM user_activity ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT user_id, action_type FROM user_activity ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT * FROM user_activity WHERE action_type='login' AND tool_used='web' ORDER BY timestamp ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT user_id, tool_used FROM user_activity WHERE session_id='123456' ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT action_type, COUNT(*) AS count FROM user_activity GROUP BY action_type HAVING count > 100
SELECT DISTINCT tool_used FROM user_activity
SELECT * FROM user_activity;
SELECT user_id, activity_description, timestamp FROM user_activity WHERE user_id = 1;
SELECT activity_id, timestamp FROM user_activity WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT user_id, COUNT(activity_id) AS total_activities FROM user_activity GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT user_id, activity_id, timestamp FROM user_activity ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, activity_id, timestamp, activity_description FROM user_activity WHERE user_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, activity_id, activity_description FROM user_activity WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY activity_id;
SELECT user_id, activity_id, timestamp FROM user_activity WHERE activity_description LIKE '%login%' ORDER BY user_id, timestamp;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(activity_id) AS total_activities FROM user_activity GROUP BY user_id HAVING total_activities > 3 ORDER BY total_activities DESC;

SELECT ua.user_id, ua.activity_id, ua.timestamp, ui.interaction_type, ui.interaction_details FROM user_activity AS ua JOIN user_interaction AS ui ON ua.user_id = ui.user_id ORDER BY ua.timestamp DESC, ui.timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_activity;
SELECT user_id, activity_type FROM user_activity WHERE activity_type = 'login';
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM user_activity WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01 00:00:00';
SELECT user_id, activity_type, activity_details->>'location' AS location FROM user_activity WHERE activity_details->>'device' = 'mobile';
SELECT user_id, MAX(timestamp) AS latest_activity_time FROM user_activity GROUP BY user_id;
SELECT * FROM user_activity;
SELECT user_id, activity_type FROM user_activity WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY user_id ASC;
SELECT board_id, board_name, created_timestamp FROM whiteboard_data WHERE board_name LIKE '%project%' ORDER BY created_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, CAST(activity_details ->> 'duration' AS INTEGER) AS duration_minutes FROM user_activity WHERE activity_details ->> 'status' = 'completed';
SELECT interaction_id, interaction_type, interaction_details FROM user_interaction WHERE interaction_type IN ('like', 'comment') ORDER BY interaction_details ->> 'timestamp' DESC;
SELECT * FROM users;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users ORDER BY username DESC;
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time FROM sessions WHERE duration > '01:00:00';
SELECT activity_type, activity_data->>'task_name' AS task_name FROM activities WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT interaction_type, interaction_data->>'action' AS action FROM interactions WHERE session_id = 456 AND timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM users ORDER BY user_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, username, email FROM users WHERE username LIKE 'A%' ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT user_id, created_at FROM users WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT u.username, s.start_time, a.activity_type FROM users u JOIN sessions s ON u.user_id = s.user_id JOIN activities a ON u.user_id = a.user_id ORDER BY s.start_time ASC;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(DISTINCT session_id) AS session_count FROM sessions GROUP BY user_id ORDER BY session_count DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, activity_type, timestamp, duration FROM UserActivity;
SELECT user_id, activity_type FROM UserActivity WHERE duration > 10;
SELECT user_id, timestamp FROM UserActivity ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT username, email, account_created_date FROM UserAccounts WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT whiteboard_id, title, owner_id FROM WhiteboardData WHERE created_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM WhiteboardData WHERE owner_id = 1 ORDER BY created_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT u.username, wa.action, uA.email FROM UserAccounts uA JOIN WhiteboardInteractions wa ON uA.user_id = wa.user_id JOIN UserAccounts u ON u.user_id = uA.user_id

SELECT ua.username, u.timestamp, wd.title FROM UserAccounts ua JOIN UserActivity u ON ua.user_id = u.user_id JOIN WhiteboardData wd ON u.user_id = wd.owner_id WHERE u.activity_type = 'Login' AND u.duration > 60
SELECT wd.title, ua.username, us.end_time FROM UserAccounts ua JOIN WhiteboardData wd ON ua.user_id = wd.owner_id JOIN UserSession us ON ua.user_id = us.user_id

SELECT uA.username, COUNT(wi.interaction_id) AS interactions_count FROM UserAccounts uA LEFT JOIN WhiteboardInteractions wi ON uA.user_id = wi.user_id GROUP BY uA.username ORDER BY interactions_count DESC
